<para style="q1">

<verse number="4" style="v" />You shine brightly and reveal your glory,</para>

<para style="q1">as you descend from the mountains, where you killed your victims.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="5" style="v" />The bravehearted were plundered;</para>

<para style="q1">they fell asleep.</para>

<para style="q1">All the warriors were helpless.</para>
